column5: Does anyone know the condition of lake Dalrymple? I'd like to go wash some lures this weekend but don't want to waste my time driving there to find ice blocking me.  Thanks in advance.

this is from Wednesday  http://coastwatch.glerl.noaa.gov/modis/modis.php?region=o&page=1&template=sub&image=t1.13107.1534.LakeOntario.143.250m.jpg  with the warm weather Thursday and Friday, I think that little ice chunk in the north end will be long gone
Cool park opens may 1st can't wait
thank you for the responses.  Never did get the chance to get out on the weekend.  Did anyone get out on Dalrymple?
